metadata.name: MOC Contributor Card #1
metadata.description: Contributor card is a commemorative Identity card issued by MOC community to outstanding contributors. At different stages of community development, there are a group of people who have made important contributions to community development. They may be members of the MOC team, MOCers, or even people who have not joined the MOC community. For different contributions, holders of Contributor card may have different rights and interests.
